    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="Fluid的其他小语法"><a href="#Fluid的其他小语法" class="headerlink" title="Fluid的其他小语法"></a>Fluid的其他小语法</h1><h2 id="1-脚注"><a href="#1-脚注" class="headerlink" title="1.脚注"></a>1.脚注</h2><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs markdown">这是脚注[^1]的用法<br>[<span class="hljs-symbol">^1</span>]: <span class="hljs-link">在一个页面底部添加的对本页某处内容的说明性文字</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：</p><p>这是脚注<sup id="fnref:1" class="footnote-ref"><a href="#fn:1" rel="footnote"><span class="hint--top hint--rounded" aria-label="在一个页面底部添加的对本页某处内容的说明性文字">[1]</span></a></sup>的用法</p><h2 id="2-便签"><a href="#2-便签" class="headerlink" title="2.便签"></a>2.便签</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ASCII">&#123;% note success %&#125;<br>文字 或者 `markdown` 均可<br>&#123;% endnote %&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>效果如下：</p><div class="note note-success">            <p>文字 或者 <code>markdown</code> 均可</p>          </div><p>以下是可选标签：</p><div class="note note-primary">            <p>primary</p>          </div><div class="note note-secondary">            <p>secondary</p>          </div><div class="note note-success">            <p>success</p>          </div><div class="note note-danger">            <p>danger</p>          </div><div class="note note-warning">            <p>warning</p>          </div><div class="note note-info">            <p>info</p>          </div><div class="note note-light">            <p>light</p>          </div><h2 id="3-行内标签"><a href="#3-行内标签" class="headerlink" title="3.行内标签"></a>3.行内标签</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ASCII">&#123;% label primary @text %&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>结果是这样滴：<span class="label label-primary">text</span></p><p>可选 Label：</p><span class="label label-primary">primary</span> <span class="label label-default">default</span><span class="label label-info">info</span><span class="label label-success">success</span><span class="label label-warning">warning</span><span class="label label-danger">danger</span><h2 id="4-折叠块"><a href="#4-折叠块" class="headerlink" title="4.折叠块"></a>4.折叠块</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ASCII">&#123;% fold info @title %&#125;<br>需要折叠的一段内容，支持 `markdown`<br>&#123;% endfold %&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>    <div class="fold">      <div class="fold-title fold-info collapsed" data-toggle="collapse" href="#collapse-82d47f7c" role="button" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse-82d47f7c">        <div class="fold-arrow">▶</div>title      </div>      <div class="fold-collapse collapse" id="collapse-82d47f7c">        <div class="fold-content">          <p>需要折叠的一段内容，支持 <code>markdown</code></p>        </div>      </div>    </div><h2 id="5-勾选框"><a href="#5-勾选框" class="headerlink" title="5.勾选框"></a>5.勾选框</h2><p>其中checked和incline填入<code>true</code>或<code>false</code></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ASCII">&#123;% cb 勾选框, checked?, incline? %&#125;<br>&#123;% btn #4-折叠块, 按钮, title %&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div>            <input type="checkbox"  checked="checked">作业写完了吗，那我问你，那我问你你作业写完了吗          </div><div>            <input type="checkbox"  >作业写完了吗，那我问你，那我问你你作业写完了吗          </div><br><a class="btn" href="#4-折叠块"  title="title" target="_blank">按钮</a><hr><h2 id="6-组图"><a href="#6-组图" class="headerlink" title="6.组图"></a>6.组图</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs ASCII">&#123;% gi total n1-n2-... %&#125;<br>  ![](url)<br>  ![](url)<br>  ![](url)<br>  ![](url)<br>  ![](url)<br>&#123;% endgi %&#125;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="group-image-container"><div class="group-image-row"><div class="group-image-wrap"><img src="/img/second_banner.jpg"></div><div class="group-image-wrap"><img src="/img/second_banner.jpg"></div><div class="group-image-wrap"><img src="/img/second_banner.jpg"></div></div><div class="group-image-row"><div class="group-image-wrap"><img src="/img/second_banner.jpg"></div><div class="group-image-wrap"><img src="/img/second_banner.jpg"></div></div><div class="group-image-row"><div class="group-image-wrap"><img src="/img/second_banner.jpg"></div></div></div><h3 id="引用"><a href="#引用" class="headerlink" title="引用"></a>引用</h3><section class="footnotes"><div class="footnote-list"><ol><li><span id="fn:1" class="footnote-text"><span>在一个页面底部添加的对本页某处内容的说明性文字<a href="#fnref:1" rev="footnote" class="footnote-backref"> ↩</a></span></span></li></ol></div></section>]]></content>
    
    
